Interface StudyChild

All Known Implementing Classes:
OtherIntervention, ReportFormat, StudyAgent, StudyCoordinatingCenter, StudyDevice, StudyFundingSponsor, StudyIntervention, StudyOrganization, StudySite, StudyTherapy, TreatmentAssignment
public interface StudyChild

This interface must be implemented by all those sub fields of Study, which are to be wrapped by LasyList. Infact the StudyChildInstantiateFactory will create the new StudyChild instance, then calls the setStudy() method.
